method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the StrokeStyle.

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyle with the specified index or name.

parameter.name: index
parameter.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByName
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyle with the specified name.

method.name: itemByID
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyle with the specified ID.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyles within the specified range.

parameter.name: from
parameter.shortdesc: The StrokeStyle, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: StrokeStyle, Long Integer or String.

parameter.name: to
parameter.shortdesc: The StrokeStyle, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: StrokeStyle, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first StrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last StrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle StrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyle with the index previous to the specified index.

parameter.name: obj
parameter.shortdesc: The index of the StrokeStyle that follows the desired StrokeStyle.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the StrokeStyle whose index follows the specified StrokeStyle in the collection.

parameter.name: obj
parameter.shortdesc: The StrokeStyle whose index comes before the desired StrokeStyle.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any StrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every StrokeStyle in the collection.

method.name: toSource
method.shortdesc: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the StrokeStyle.
Returns the StrokeStyle with the specified index.
